er you have at your disposal while The Queen is trying to finish her ritual. Build traps to get assistance from Lich Queen's servants and use your powers to stop the king's army. If you lose a trap, fret not! With scraps you get from traps that you destroyed, you can build better and stronger traps. Use the enemy souls for progress in your perk tree and become a better general to try new strategies! Strategize, be active and keep your eyes on the battlefield to make sure to win enough time for your Queen!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693480/extras/4a1c3c4df4c10c82ec674f844c049507.avif?t=1646377767\" width=592 height=96 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693480/extras/751ec7e84a0de572976246d4bb42bd95.poster.avif?t=1646377767\" width=592 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693480/extras/751ec7e84a0de572976246d4bb42bd95.webm?t=1646377767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693480/extras/751ec7e84a0de572976246d4bb42bd95.mp4?t=1646377767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
